  "detailed_description": "VR Action Game for Valve Index. And Hey, its not a Wave Shooter! <br>About 20min to 40min long, self contained Adventure of oldscool Action.<br>Free locomotion with zero assist (thats a feature).<br>All the Reloading you would want in a VR game.<br>Pumpgun is reloaded through rotation like in T2.<br><strong>The demo Version is the same as the paid Version, so play that, and if you had <br>fun consider supporting me with the paid Version.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560510/extras/1b6592df7c1cd029cdcb16262318f896.poster.avif?t=1615501937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560510/extras/1b6592df7c1cd029cdcb16262318f896.webm?t=1615501937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560510/extras/1b6592df7c1cd029cdcb16262318f896.mp4?t=1615501937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>special thanks to E and Coco!",
